description: Delight your guests with creative canapes. Flaky puff pastry with three delectable fillings of chicken and avocado, blue cheese and honey, and choc-berry.
name: Vol-Au-Vents Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Bake vol-au-vents for 5 minutes or until warmed through. Top chicken vol-au-vents with avocado, onion and parsley, and cheese vol-au-vents with pear, blueberries, thyme and extra honey. Serve.
